    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/ba96850a2cfa710df836fd786f55c45c.avif?t=1730455737\" width=617 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >飞行、瞬移、跳墙，通过难度越来越高的关卡。有了扫帚、帽子和魔法鞋，你就能解锁各种超能力，让每一个动作都令人振奋。掌握飞行的艺术，发现超越一切障碍的新方法。不过要小心，扫帚可能会失灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/46874153661d19e3e54b09df4680145f.poster.avif?t=1730455737\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/46874153661d19e3e54b09df4680145f.webm?t=1730455737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/46874153661d19e3e54b09df4680145f.mp4?t=1730455737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/c0aabc5d8efdf5ac21e332311722bfe0.avif?t=1730455737\" width=617 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在与年轻女巫罗宾不期而遇后，玛雅踏上了自我发现之旅。她们一起追捕被施了魔法的失控打印机，面对魔法挑战，揭开一路上的秘密。玛雅会学会接受真正的自己吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/44e87cf83c61120436673f7624e5579e.poster.avif?t=1730455737\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/44e87cf83c61120436673f7624e5579e.webm?t=1730455737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/44e87cf83c61120436673f7624e5579e.mp4?t=1730455737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/8aafb763b586a8903b63074e83af7ccf.avif?t=1730455737\" width=617 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都充满了秘密和隐藏的咒语书页，旨在考验您的技能。您可能会失败，但每一次重试都会让您更接近掌握玛雅的力量，并夺回每一件收藏品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/b0c62a0a917acc87c74a57e6773828c9.poster.avif?t=1730455737\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/b0c62a0a917acc87c74a57e6773828c9.webm?t=1730455737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/b0c62a0a917acc87c74a57e6773828c9.mp4?t=1730455737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/a540a0ee7c2c4c26d07030d87d2a8d3c.avif?t=1730455737\" width=617 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从阴森恐怖的下水道深处，到生机勃勃的城市街道，再到隐藏在云层中的危险，每个关卡都提供了独特的氛围和惊心动魄的挑战。每前进一步，都会有新的东西等待您去探索！您能到达漂浮在高空中的女巫之城吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/27e0671f6d69d013199f98bc51c2aaaf.poster.avif?t=1730455737\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/27e0671f6d69d013199f98bc51c2aaaf.webm?t=1730455737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823030/extras/27e0671f6d69d013199f98bc51c2aaaf.mp4?t=1730455737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
